snippet.title: Foglight Online Trailer (1 v 6 Horror Multiplayer Game)
snippet.description:
February 4th
Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1517520/Foglight_Online/
Discord https://discord.gg/dCysxNEKkc

Foglight Online is a 1 v 6 player horror game. One player plays as the monster Farberto and must track down the other players uses their scent. The other players either have to fight back or escape.
